          "type": "text",
          "text": "6. Performance Considerations"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The performance of this scalar function is generally efficient due to its simplicity. The function involves basic arithmetic operations and the "
